%20an%20opportunity%20to%20burnish%20their%20credentials%20as%20the%20champions%20of%20the%20developing%20world%2C%20in%20contrast%20with%20the%20United%20States%2C%20which%20has%20put%20its%20support%20squarely%20behind%20ally%20Israel.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EChina%20has%20consistently%20called%20for%20restraint%20and%20a%20ceasefire%20but%20has%20also%20sharpened%20its%20criticism%20of%20Israel.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIsrael's%20actions%20have%20gone%20beyond%20the%20scope%20of%20self-defence%2C%26quot%3B%20Chinese%20Foreign%20Minister%20Wang%20Yi%20said%20this%20week%2C%20calling%20on%20it%20to%20stop%20its%20%26quot%3Bcollective%20punishment%26quot%3B%20of%20Gaza%20residents%2C%20Chinese%20state%20media%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ERussia%20has%20expressed%20sympathy%20for%20the%20Palestinians%20while%20blaming%20the%20US%20%26quot%3BI%20think%20that%20many%20people%20will%20agree%20with%20me%20that%20this%20is%20a%20vivid%20example%20of%20the%20failure%20of%20United%20States%20policy%20in%20the%20Middle%20East%2C%26quot%3B%20Russian%20President%20Vladimir%20Putin%20said%20this%20week.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBoth%20Putin%20and%20Chinese%20President%20Xi%20Jinping%20have%20sought%20to%20deepen%20ties%20to%20the%20global%20south%2C%20seeing%20economic%20opportunities%20and%20possibly%20a%20way%20to%20counterbalance%20the%20diplomatic%20influence%20of%20the%20US%20and%20its%20allies.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThat%20was%20on%20display%20this%20week%20as%20China%20hosted%20a%20summit%20for%20Xi's%20signature%20Belt%20and%20Road%20Initiative%2C%20which%20has%20lent%20hundreds%20of%20billions%20of%20dollars%20for%20infrastructure%20projects%20across%20the%20Middle%20East%2C%20Africa%2C%20Latin%20America%20and%20Asia.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EPutin%20attended%20and%20met%20Xi%20for%20three%20hours%20of%20talks%20that%20included%20%26quot%3Ban%20in-depth%20exchange%20of%20views%20on%20the%20Palestinian-Israeli%20situation%26quot%3B%2C%20China%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BChina%20and%20Russia%20still%20see%20(the%20crisis)%20more%20in%20terms%20of%20the%20United%20States%20than%20in%20terms%20of%20either%20Palestine%20or%20Israel%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Jon%20Alterman%2C%20director%20of%20the%20Middle%20East%20Program%20at%20the%20Center%20for%20Strategic%20and%20International%20Studies%20in%20Washington.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20the%20United%20States%20can%20effectively%20rally%20the%20world%2C%20it's%20bad%20for%20them.%20If%20the%20US%20and%20its%20allies%20grow%20increasingly%20isolated%2C%20they%20see%20that%20as%20good%20for%20them.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3ESupport%20For%20Palestine%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%20%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20strategies%20of%20Russia%20and%20China%20in%20the%20Middle%20East%20are%20not%20fully%20aligned%20they%20have%20much%20in%20common.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ERussia%20is%20sharply%20critical%20of%20the%20US%20but%20China%20has%20mostly%20avoided%20criticising%20it%2C%20a%20contrast%20to%20early%20in%20the%20Ukraine%20war%2C%20when%20China's%20support%20of%20Russia%20turned%20an%20unwelcome%20spotlight%20on%20its%20diplomatic%20position.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EChina%20signalled%20its%20growing%20influence%20in%20the%20Middle%20East%20this%20year%20when%20it%20announced%20a%20surprise%20deal%20on%20the%20restoration%20of%20ties%20between%20Saudi%20Arabia%20and%20Iran.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ERussia%20too%20has%20been%20improving%20ties%20with%20Iran%2C%20which%20has%20included%20supplies%20of%20Iranian%20drones%20and%20common%20cause%20in%20backing%20Syrian%20President%20Bashar%20al-Assad.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBoth%20China%20and%20Russia%20share%20a%20history%20of%20support%20for%20the%20Palestinians%20-%20and%20are%20critical%20of%20what%20they%20say%20is%20the%20marginalisation%20of%20them%20by%20the%20United%20States.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere's%20clearly%20a%20shared%20interest%20in%20emphasizing%20the%20negative%20role%20of%20the%20US%20in%20the%20conflict%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Jean-Loup%20Samaan%2C%20senior%20research%20fellow%20at%20the%20Middle%20East%20Institute%20of%20the%20National%20University%20of%20Singapore.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAnd%20that%20fits%20within%20their%20broader%20narrative%20on%20the%20need%20to%20build%20an%20alternative%20world%20order%20to%20the%20US%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ERussia's%20state%20media%20has%20said%20it%20was%20sending%20humanitarian%20aid%20to%20Gaza%20and%20China%20has%20sent%20its%20Middle%20East%20envoy%20to%20the%20region%2C%20where%20he%20met%20Russia's%20special%20representative.%20Russia%20said%20on%20Thursday%20it%20was%20coordinating%20Middle%20East%20policy%20with%20China.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWhile%20Chinese%20media%20covered%20the%20Hamas%20attacks%20on%20October%207%2C%20since%20then%20reports%20have%20carried%20images%20of%20Palestinian%20suffering%2C%20with%20some%20prominently%20citing%20Palestinian%20sources%20as%20saying%20Israel%20was%20responsible.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNone%20of%20the%20reality%20that%20shocked%20much%20of%20the%20world%20on%20October%207%20is%20in%20Chinese%20news.%20Instead%2C%20the%20news%20features%20Israeli%20bombing%20of%20Gaza%20without%20explaining%20that%20the%20target%20is%20only%20Hamas%20infrastructure%2C%26quot%3B%20Carice%20Witte%2C%20director%20of%20the%20SIGNAL%20Group%2C%20a%20Sino-Israel%20relations%20think%20tank%20based%20in%20Tel%20Aviv.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3ESeeking%20Allies%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%20%3Cp%3ERussia's%20war%20in%20Ukraine%20gives%20it%20an%20added%20incentive%20to%20align%20itself%20with%20the%20Palestinian%20cause.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20United%20States%20has%20been%20trying%2C%20with%20limited%20success%2C%20to%20persuade%20the%20global%20south%20to%20rally%20behind%20Ukraine.%20Portraying%20the%20US%20as%20a%20driver%20of%20the%20conflict%20helps%20blunt%20that%20effort.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAlterman%20sees%20a%20similar%20motivation%20for%20China%2C%20which%20regards%20the%20U.S.%20as%20its%20chief%20geopolitical%20rival.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BChina%20is%20trying%20to%20play%20the%20global%20south%20card%2C%20irrespective%20of%20its%20close%20ties%20to%20Israel.%20More%20than%20actually%20supporting%20Hamas%2C%20it%20is%20quietly%20helping%20build%20resistance%20to%20US%20efforts%20to%20build%20international%20support%20for%20Israel%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Alterman.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMa%20Xiaolin%2C%20a%20Middle%20East%20expert%20and%20professor%20at%20Zhejiang%20International%20Studies%20University%2C%20said%20China%20was%20being%20even-handed%20between%20the%20Palestinians%20and%20Israel%20but%20if%20pushed%2C%20would%20side%20with%20its%20Arab%20partners.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20Israel%2C%20with%20the%20support%20of%20the%20United%20States%2C%20expands%20the%20scale%20and%20scope%20of%20the%20war%20and%20causes%20more%20humanitarian%20casualties%2C%20China%20will%20definitely%20tilt%20the%20balance%20in%20favour%20of%20the%20Palestinians%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Ma.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1697802900000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2022-09%2F87g0lauo_putin-xi_625x300_16_September_22.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fisrael-palestine-war-how-russia-china-found-common-cause-in-israel-hamas-war-4499427%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22With%20anger%20building%20across%20the%20Middle%20East%20over%20Israel's%20strikes%20in%20Gaza%2C%20China%20and%20Russia%20are%20finding%20common%20cause%20with%20countries%20across%20the%20region%20in%20support%20of%20the%20Palestinians.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fisrael-palestine-war-how-russia-china-found-common-cause-in-israel-hamas-war-4499427%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fisrael-palestine-war-how-russia-china-found-common-cause-in-israel-hamas-war-4499427%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fisrael-palestine-war-how-russia-china-found-common-cause-in-israel-hamas-war-4499427%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22To%20Prepare%20For%20Gaganyaan%20Success%2C%20ISRO%20Will%20Test%20A%20Failure%20Tomorrow%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIt's%20going%20to%20be%20a%20flight%20of%20failure%2C%20which%20will%20set%20up%20ISRO%20for%20success.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAttempting%20to%20prepare%20for%20every%20possibility%2C%20which%20is%20now%20a%20part%20of%20its%20ethos%2C%20the%20Indian%20Space%20Research%20Organisation%20will%20carry%20out%20an%20abort%20test%20for%20the%20human%20space%20mission%2C%20Gaganyaan%2C%20on%20Saturday.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EA%20similar%20fail-safe%20approach%20had%20been%20taken%20for%20Chandrayaan-3%20and%20had%20helped%20ISRO%20script%20history%20by%20making%20India%20the%20first%20country%20to%20land%20nearer%20the%20south%20pole%20of%20the%20Moon%20in%20August.%20The%20stakes%2C%20though%2C%20are%20much%20higher%20this%20time%20because%20the%20lives%20of%20humans%20will%20be%20involved.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20exclusively%20to%20NDTV%2C%20Dr%20Unnikrishnan%20Nair%2C%20director%20of%20the%20Vikram%20Sarabhai%20Space%20Centre%2C%20which%20is%20an%20ISRO%20research%20centre%2C%20said%20the%20most%20important%20thing%20for%20the%20agency%20in%20the%20Gaganyaan%20mission%20is%20the%20safety%20of%20the%20crew.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20first%20mission%20is%20demonstrating%20the%20crew%20escape%20system%20during%20flight.%20We%20should%20ensure%20that%2C%20at%20any%20stage%20during%20the%20ascent%20phase%2C%20if%20anything%20goes%20wrong%20with%20the%20vehicle%2C%20the%20safety%20of%20the%20crew%20is%20ensured.%20The%20crew%20escape%20system%2C%20which%20will%20operate%20during%20the%20first%20stage%20of%20the%20vehicle%2C%20has%20to%20work%20in%20different%20conditions%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20test%20is%20scheduled%20for%208%20am%20from%20the%20first%20launchpad%20of%20the%20Satish%20Dhawan%20Space%20Centre%20in%20Sriharikota.%20The%20crew%20escape%20system%2C%20which%20will%20have%20the%20unpressurised%20crew%20module%20housing%20the%20astronauts%20during%20the%20actual%20Gaganyaan%20flight%2C%20will%20be%20fixed%20atop%20the%20test%20vehicle.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20the%20vehicle%20reaches%20an%20altitude%20of%2012%20km%20and%20achieves%20the%20transonic%20condition%2C%20the%20thrust%20of%20the%20vehicle%20will%20be%20terminated%20and%20motors%20of%20the%20escape%20system%20will%20be%20activated.%20That%20will%20take%20the%20crew%20module%20plus%20crew%20escape%20system%20to%20an%20altitude%20of%20about%2017%20km.%20At%20that%20altitude%2C%20the%20crew%20module%20will%20be%20released%20from%20the%20escape%20system%2C%26quot%3B%20Dr%20Nair%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20the%20crew%20module%20has%20been%20designed%20in%20a%20way%20that%20it%20can%20turn%20by%20itself%20and%20orient%20itself%20in%20the%20required%20direction.%20Once%20that%20is%20done%2C%20parachutes%20will%20be%20deployed%20and%20the%20module%20will%20drop%20slowly%20into%20the%20sea%20about%2010%20km%20from%20the%20launch%20pad.%20The%20crew%20escape%20system%20and%20the%20launch%20vehicle%20will%20also%20fall%20into%20the%20sea%2C%20but%20at%20a%20distance%20from%20the%20crew%20module.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20entire%20test%20is%20expected%20to%20last%20about%20nine%20minutes.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EGaganyaan%2C%20which%20is%20expected%20to%20launch%20in%202025%2C%20aims%20to%20take%20a%20crew%20of%203%20members%20to%20an%20orbit%20of%20400%20km%20for%20a%203-day%20mission%20and%20bring%20them%20back%20safely%20to%20Earth%20by%20landing%20in%20Indian%20waters.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1697802540000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-10%2Fbctpr978_gaganyaan-first-test_625x300_20_October_23.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fto-prepare-for-gaganyaan-success-isro-will-test-a-failure-tomorrow-4499994%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Attempting%20to%20prepare%20for%20every%20possibility%2C%20which%20is%20now%20a%20part%20of%20its%20ethos%2C%20the%20Indian%20Space%20Research%20Organisation%20will%20carry%20out%20an%20abort%20test%20for%20the%20human%20space%20mission%2C%20Gaganyaan%2C%20on%20Saturday.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A7%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fto-prepare-for-gaganyaan-success-isro-will-test-a-failure-tomorrow-4499994%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fto-prepare-for-gaganyaan-success-isro-will-test-a-failure-tomorrow-4499994%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fto-prepare-for-gaganyaan-success-isro-will-test-a-failure-tomorrow-4499994%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22In%20Mission%20To%20Send%20Indian%20To%20Moon%2C%20Gaganyaan's%201st%20Big%20Test%20Tomorrow%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ERiding%20on%20the%20huge%20success%20of%20Chandrayaan-3%2C%20India%20is%20now%20taking%20baby%20steps%20towards%20the%20ambitious%20Gaganyaan%20mission.%20On%20Saturday%2C%20Gaganyaan's%20crew%20module%20escape%20system%20will%20be%20live%20tested%20from%20Sriharikota.%20This%20is%20the%20first%20of%20the%2020%20big%20tests%20that%20ISRO%20has%20planned%20for%20the%20near%20future.%20All%20in%20an%20effort%20to%20meet%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi's%20target%20that%20ISRO%20sets%20up%20an%20Indian%20Space%20Station%20to%20by%202035%20and%20launch%20Indian%20astronaut%20to%20the%20Moon%20by%202040.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EDr%20Unnikrishnan%20Nair%2C%20Director%2C%20Vikram%20Sarabhai%20Space%20Center%2C%20ISRO%20-%20a%20key%20player%20in%20India's%20human%20space%20program%20says%2C%20%26quot%3BGaganyaan%20is%20challenging%20but%20very%20doable%20as%20India%20has%20all%20the%20necessary%20technology%20and%20Rs%209%2C000%20crore%20have%20already%20been%20sanctioned%20by%20the%20government%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EPrime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20has%20already%20announced%20that%20New%20Delhi%20will%20set%20up%20an%20Indian%20Space%20Station%20by%202035%20and%20send%20an%20'Indian%20to%20Moon%20by%202040'.%20Nair%20says%2C%20%26quot%3BHumans%20will%20inhabit%20the%20moon%20sooner%20than%20later%20and%20India%20a%20country%20of%201.4%20billion%20can't%20be%20left%20behind%20so%20ISRO%20is%20preparing%20to%20give%20India%20independent%20access%20to%20space%20for%20its%20citizens%20on%20its%20own%20steam%26quot%3B.%20PM%20Modi%20in%20a%20statement%20said%20%26quot%3Bto%20realise%20this%20Vision%2C%20the%20Department%20of%20Space%20will%20develop%20a%20roadmap%20for%20Moon%20exploration.%20This%20will%20encompass%20a%20series%20of%20Chandrayaan%20missions%2C%20the%20development%20of%20a%20Next%20Generation%20Launch%20Vehicle%20(NGLV)%2C%20construction%20of%20a%20new%20launch%20pad%2C%20setting%20up%20human-centric%20Laboratories%20and%20associated%20technologies.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EA%20crucial%20test%20of%20the%20Gaganyaan%20mission%20will%20answer%20some%20crucial%20questions.%20What%20happens%20to%20our%20astronauts%20if%20things%20go%20wrong%3F%20Will%20the%20test%20capsule%20separate%20from%20the%20rocket%3F%20Will%20emergency%20parachutes%20open%2C%20before%20the%20crew%20escape%20system%20lands%20in%20the%20Indian%20Ocean%3F%20The%20Indian%20space%20agency%20will%20conduct%20a%20crew%20escape%20system%20test%20-%20an%20important%20test%20to%20prove%20the%20safety%20of%20the%20rocket%20before%20humans%20can%20be%20orbited.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20ambitious%20Gaganyaan%20program%2C%20ISRO%20hopes%20to%20launch%20an%20Indian%20astronaut%20into%20space%20from%20Indian%20soil%20on%20an%20Indian%20rocket%20sometime%20after%202024.%20The%20Indian%20crew%20module%20can%20accommodate%20three%20astronauts%20who%20can%20then%20have%20a%20mission%20of%20up%20to%20a%20week%20in%20a%20low%20earth%20orbit.%20The%20crew%20module%20is%20likely%20to%20be%20tested%20on%20a%20new%20rocket%20initially%20without%20housing%20any%20astronauts%20and%20an%20abort%20test%20will%20be%20conducted%20at%20an%20altitude%20of%2017%20kilometres%20and%20the%20crew%20module%20will%20be%20recovered%20from%20the%20Bay%20of%20Bengal%20by%20the%20Indian%20Navy.%20Many%20tests%20like%20this%20will%20be%20conducted%20and%20if%20nearly%20two%20dozen%20or%20more%20of%20these%20big%20tests%20are%20successful%2C%20then%20any%20of%20the%20four%20designated%20astronauts%20will%20be%20flown.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EGaganyaan%20Mission%20will%20launch%20an%20Indian%20astronaut%20into%20space%20from%20Sriharikota.%20Crew%20Escape%20System%20will%20be%20tested%20soon%20before%20humans%20can%20be%20flown.%20The%20module%20can%20accommodate%20a%20crew%20of%20three%20for%20about%20a%20week%20in%20space.%20The%20Crew%20Module%20has%20been%20designed%20by%20ISRO%20and%20it%20is%20Indian.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ELaunch%20Vehicle%20Mark%20-3%20the%20chosen%20rocket%20is%20now%20human-rated.%20Four%20astronauts%20have%20been%20trained%2C%20all%20four%20are%20Indian%20Air%20Force%20(IAF)%20test%20pilots%20and%20all%20four%20in%20the%20maiden%20cohort%20are%20men%20as%20there%20were%20no%20female%20test%20pilots%20in%20India.%20Nair%20says%20%26quot%3BWomen%20can%20be%20accommodated%20in%20the%20future%20as%20ISRO%20is%20gender%20agnostic%20and%20only%20talent%20matters%26quot%3B.%20In%20the%20Gaganyaan%20Mission%2C%20Russian-made%20flight%20suits%20will%20be%20used%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBut%20ISRO's%20ambitious%20Gaganyaan%20Mission%20to%20send%20an%20Indian%20astronaut%20into%20space%20is%20giving%20the%20scientists%20working%20on%20it%20sleepless%20nights%20since%20this%20will%20be%20the%20first%20time%20ISRO%20will%20launch%20an%20Indian%20into%20space.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EDr%20Unnikrishnan%20Nair%20says%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%20astronauts%20will%20bring%20glory%20to%20India%2C%20and%20if%20India%20succeeds%20it%20will%20become%20the%20fourth%20country%20to%20have%20independent%20capability%20to%20send%20humans%20to%20space%20after%20Russia%2C%20USA%20and%20China.%26quot%3B%20%26quot%3BI%20am%20not%20tense%20about%20Gaganyaan%2C%20we%20need%20to%20do%20our%20homework%20properly%20but%20Gaganyaan%20will%20certainly%20cause%20skipping%20of%20heartbeats%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1697802480000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-10%2Faioufdp4_gaganyaan-mission-ani_625x300_20_October_23.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fgaganyaan-in-mission-to-send-indian-to-moon-gaganyaans-1st-big-test-tomorrow-4499877%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Riding%20on%20the%20huge%20success%20of%20Chandrayaan-3%2C%20India%20is%20now%20taking%20baby%20steps%20towards%20the%20ambitious%20Gaganyaan%20mission.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A2%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fgaganyaan-in-mission-to-send-indian-to-moon-gaganyaans-1st-big-test-tomorrow-4499877%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fgaganyaan-in-mission-to-send-indian-to-moon-gaganyaans-1st-big-test-tomorrow-4499877%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fgaganyaan-in-mission-to-send-indian-to-moon-gaganyaans-1st-big-test-tomorrow-4499877%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22New%20MCC%20Rule%20That%20May%20Have%20Helped%20Kohli%20Score%20His%2048th%20ODI%20Ton%20-%20Explained%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Virat%20Kohli%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F967-virat-kohli-playerprofile%5C%22%3EVirat%20Kohli%3C%2Fa%3E%20slammed%20a%20brilliant%20century%20to%20guide%20the%20Indian%20cricket%20team%20to%20a%20comfortable%20victory%20over%20Bangladesh%20in%20the%20Cricket%20World%20Cup%202023%20on%20Thursday%20but%20a%20controversial%20decision%20by%20umpire%20Richard%20Kettleborough%20became%20a%20major%20talking%20point%20after%20the%20match.%20With%20Kohli%20batting%20on%2097%20and%20India%20needing%20two%20runs%20to%20win%2C%20Bangladesh%20bowler%20Nasum%20Ahmed%20fired%20a%20delivery%20towards%20the%20leg%20stump.%20Kohli%20shuffled%20a%20bit%20towards%20the%20stumps%20and%20the%20wicket-keeper%20collected%20it%20on%20the%20leg%20side.%20However%2C%20the%20umpire%20decided%20to%20not%20award%20a%20wide%20to%20India%20and%20instead%2C%20the%20delivery%20was%20judged%20to%20be%20a%20dot%20ball.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EKohli%20went%20on%20to%20score%20his%2048th%20ODI%20century%20with%20a%20massive%20six%20just%20two%20balls%20after%20this%20incident.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWhile%20fans%20were%20left%20confused%20by%20the%20umpire's%20decision%20to%20not%20award%20the%20wide%20despite%20the%20wicket-keeper%20collecting%20the%20ball%20on%20the%20leg%20side%2C%20the%20reason%20was%20a%20rule%20change%20by%20Marylebone%20Cricket%20Club%20in%202022.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20the%20modern%20game%2C%20batters%20are%2C%20more%20than%20ever%2C%20moving%20laterally%20around%20the%20crease%20before%20the%20ball%20is%20bowled.%20It%20was%20felt%20unfair%20that%20a%20delivery%20might%20be%20called%20%E2%80%98Wide'%20if%20it%20passes%20where%20the%20batter%20had%20stood%20as%20the%20bowler%20entered%20his%2Fher%20delivery%20stride.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTherefore%2C%20Law%2022.1%20has%20been%20amended%20so%20that%20a%20Wide%20will%20apply%20to%20where%20the%20batter%20is%20standing%2C%20where%20the%20striker%20has%20stood%20at%20any%20point%20since%20the%20bowler%20began%20their%20run-up%2C%20and%20which%20would%20also%20have%20passed%20wide%20of%20the%20striker%20in%20a%20normal%20batting%20position%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20amended%20rule%20stated.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20rule%20was%20brought%20in%20to%20make%20sure%20that%20bowlers%20are%20not%20punished%20for%20batters%20moving%20across%20the%20stumps%20just%20when%20the%20ball%20is%20delivered.%20As%20a%20result%2C%20Kohli's%20batting%20stance%20kept%20him%20outside%20the%20line%20of%20the%20leg%20stump%20and%20when%20he%20shuffled%20across%2C%20the%20umpire%20judged%20it%20to%20be%20a%20change%20of%20position%20by%20the%20batter.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1697802240000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-10%2Ftostkqog_virat_625x300_20_October_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Ficc-cricket-world-cup-2023%2Fnew-mcc-rule-that-may-have-helped-virat-kohli-score-his-48th-odi-ton-explained-4499683%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20controversial%20decision%20by%20umpire%20Richard%20Kettleborough%20involving%20Virat%20Kohli%20became%20a%20major%20talking%20point%20after%20the%20Cricket%20World%20Cup%202023%20match%20between%20India%20and%20Bangladesh.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A31%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Ficc-cricket-world-cup-2023%2Fnew-mcc-rule-that-may-have-helped-virat-kohli-score-his-48th-odi-ton-explained-4499683%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Ficc-cricket-world-cup-2023%2Fnew-mcc-rule-that-may-have-helped-virat-kohli-score-his-48th-odi-ton-explained-4499683%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Ficc-cricket-world-cup-2023%2Fnew-mcc-rule-that-may-have-helped-virat-kohli-score-his-48th-odi-ton-explained-4499683%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Money%20laundering%3A%20Sanjay%20Singh's%20plea%20dismissed%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1697802053000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-104584768%2Cimgsize-669276.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fcity%2Fdelhi%2Fmoney-