glish%20poet%20should%20be%20allowed%20to%20handle.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHenry%2C%20the%20Rottweiler.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EPope%20would%20have%20written%20a%20mock-epic%20about%20the%20life%20and%20times%20of%20this%20magnificent%20dog%20who%20may%2C%20or%20may%20not%2C%20end%20up%20bringing%20down%20political%20and%20legal%20careers%2C%20industrial%20houses%2C%20and%20even%20governments.%20All%20animals%20are%20equal%20but%20some%20are%20more%20equal%20than%20others.%20Henry%20is%20that%20extraordinary%20beast%20who%20may%20go%20down%20in%20history%20for%20causing%20one%20of%20the%20most%20lurid%20political%20scandals%20of%20our%20times.%20Something%20that%20merits%20a%20sequel%20of%20Pope's%201712%20poem%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Rape%20of%20the%20Lock.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHenry's%20human%20parents%20were%20once%20together%20and%20he%20had%20a%20happy%20home%20-%20safe%20from%20all%20the%20bad%20press%20his%20%26quot%3Baggressive%26quot%3B%20breed%20has%20been%20receiving%20of%20late.%20Henry%2C%20the%20gentle%20giant%2C%20has%20his%20own%20Instagram%20account%2C%20in%20the%20true%20tradition%20of%2021st-century%20beau%20monde.%20But%20someone%20has%20cast%20their%20evil%20eye%20on%20Henry.%20Yeah%2C%20even%20dogs%20are%20not%20safe%20from%20the%20voyeuristic%20bad%20energies%20of%20people%20who%20claim%20to%20be%20'friends'%20but%20really%20aren't.%20Yes%2C%20those%20very%20people%20who%20look%20at%20your%20posts%20only%20to%20find%20something%20you%20can%20be%20ridiculed%20about%20behind%20your%20back.%20This%20bad%20breed%20struck%20poor%20Henry%20and%20his%20parents%20separated%2C%20and%20what%20followed%20next%20would%20have%20shocked%20even%20Homer%20or%20Valmiki.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EPope%2C%20however%2C%20would%20have%20rubbed%20his%20hands%20in%20glee%20and%20gone%20on%20to%20write%20about%20individualism%20that%20can%20only%20assert%20itself%20through%20material%20acquisitions.%20He'd%20have%20called%20an%20emergency%20meeting%20of%20his%20Scriblerus%20Club%20to%20discuss%20the%20alleged%20matter%20of%20scarves%2C%20handbags%2C%20iPhones%20and%20accessories%2C%20on%20one%20hand%2C%20and%20the%20fury%20and%20pathos%20of%20a%20jilted%20lover%20on%20the%20other.%20Of%20course%2C%20Pope%20would%20not%20have%20taken%20any%20prisoners%20and%20mercilessly%20attacked%20the%20smallness%20of%20big%20people.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWhat%20Pope%20would%20have%20also%20done%2C%20through%20his%20fine%20lines%20of%20satire%2C%20is%20showing%20that%20institutions%20and%20individuals%20can%20only%20be%20brought%20down%20from%20within.%C2%A0That%20it%20takes%20only%20one%20collaborator%2C%20like%20Clarissa%20in%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Rape%20of%20the%20Lock%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20for%20all%20hell%20to%20break%20loose.%20When%20the%20integrity%20of%20any%20institution%20or%20individual%20is%20exposed%20to%20be%20as%20delicate%20as%20an%20Hermes%20scarf%2C%20claws%20come%20out%20on%20all%20sides.%20It%20takes%20a%20Henry%20to%20create%20one%20such%20collaborator.%20While%20FIRs%2C%20affidavits%2C%20defamation%20suits%2C%20and%20their%20counters%20continued%20to%20emerge%20in%20the%20public%20domain%2C%20Pope%20would%20have%20set%20his%20eyes%20on%20Henry%2C%20the%20mute%20witness%20to%20a%20distasteful%20farce%20around%20his%20custody%20that%20has%20now%20engulfed%20multiple%20political%20parties%2C%20industrial%20houses%2C%20high%20net%20worth%20individuals%2C%20and%20many%20a%20personal%20relationship.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EDoes%20Henry%20want%20to%20be%20dragged%20into%20this%20circus%20of%20human%20follies%20and%20foibles%3F%20Probably%20not.%20Does%20he%20want%20his%20legs%20massaged%3F%20Maybe%20yes!%20Does%20he%20want%20his%20Daddy%20around%3F%20Who%20is%20to%20say%3F%20Poor%20Henry%20is%20no%20Callie%2C%20the%20adopted%20dog%20of%20neuroscientist%20Gregory%20Berns%20who%20collaborated%20with%20her%20Daddy%20when%20he%20wanted%20to%20use%20his%20decades-long%20experience%20of%20using%20MRI%20imaging%20technology%20to%20study%20how%20the%20human%20brain%20w