.com%2Ffeature%2Fanshul-jubli-to-make-ufc-debut-on-oct-21-5-facts-on-indian-mma-fighter-4499449%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Anshul%20Jubli%2C%20the%20mixed%20martial%20arts%20(MMA)%20fighter%20from%20India%2C%20will%20make%20his%20official%20debut%20in%20Ultimate%20Fighting%20Championship%20(UFC)%20on%20October%2021%20(Saturday)%20in%20Abu%20Dhabi.%20He%20will%20take%20on%20American%20lightweight%20Mike%20Breeden.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Fanshul-jubli-to-make-ufc-debut-on-oct-21-5-facts-on-indian-mma-fighter-4499449%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Nithari%20Killings%20Accused%20Released%20From%20Jail%2C%20Another%20To%20Remain%20Behind%20Bars%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ENithari's%20serial%20killings'%20accused%20Moninder%20Singh%20Pandhar%20was%20released%20from%20a%20Greater%20Noida%20jail%20today%20days%20after%20the%20Allahabad%20high%20Court%20cleared%20him%20of%20all%20charges.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Allahabad%20High%20Court%20on%20Monday%20acquitted%20Moninder%20Singh%20Pandhar%20in%20two%20cases%20and%20his%20domestic%20help%20Surendra%20Koli%20-%20who%20is%20the%20main%20accused%20in%20the%20sensational%20case%20-%20in%2012%20cases.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESurinder%20Koli%20and%20Moninder%20Singh%20Pandher%2C%20who%20were%20convicted%20of%20rape%20and%20murder%2C%20were%20acquitted%20by%20the%20high%20court%20over%20lack%20of%20evidence.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20high%20court%20said%20the%20prosecution%20had%20failed%20to%20prove%20its%20case%20beyond%20reasonable%20doubt.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EKoli%2C%20however%2C%20continues%20to%20be%20a%20life-term%20prisoner%20for%20his%20conviction%20in%20one%20case.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20serial%20killings%20took%20place%20at%20Moninder%20Pandher's%20home%20in%20Nithari%20area%20of%20Uttar%20Pradesh's%20Noida%20between%202005%20and%202006%2C%20according%20to%20the%20CBI.%3C%2Fp%3E%20