0war%2C%20Israel%20has%20started%20evacuating%20some%2023.000%20citizens%20of%20Kiryat%20Shemona.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20another%20development%20believed%20to%20be%20connected%20to%20Israel's%20war%20against%20Hamas%2C%20US%20bases%20were%20hit%20by%20drone%20attacks%20in%20Iraq%20on%20Thursday.%20Two%20drones%20targeted%20the%20al%20Asad%20airbase%20in%20western%20Iraq%20used%20by%20US%20forces%20and%20one%20targeted%20a%20base%20in%20the%20country's%20north%20near%20the%20city%20of%20Erbil.%20US%20forces%20intercepted%20all%20three%2C%20destroying%20two%20but%20only%20damaging%20the%20third%2C%20which%20led%20to%20minor%20injuries%20among%20coalition%20forces%20at%20the%20western%20base.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThese%20attacks%20on%20US%20bases%20are%20widely%20believed%20to%20have%20been%20carried%20out%20by%20pro-Iranian%20Shiite%20militia%20forces%20operating%20in%20Iraq.%20And%20they%20are%20seen%20as%20a%20part%20of%20Iran's%20effort%20to%20deter%20Israel%20and%20the%20US%20from%20setting%20in%20motion%20a%20land%20invasion%20of%20Gaza.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIran's%20Foreign%20Minister%20Amir%20Abdollahian%20warned%20earlier%20this%20week%20that%20Iran%20has%20%26quot%3Bred%20lines%26quot%3B%2C%20that%20if%20Israel's%20attacks%20continued%20and%20if%20a%20land%20attack%20on%20Gaza%20was%20launched%2C%20Iran%20%26quot%3Bwill%20have%20to%20respond.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20press%20release%2C%20the%20US%20Central%20Command%20in%20Iraq%20commented%20on%20the%20latest%20escalation.%26quot%3BIn%20this%20moment%20of%20heightened%20alert%2C%20we%20are%20vigilantly%20monitoring%20the%20situation%20in%20Iraq%20and%20the%20region.%20US%20forces%20will%20defend%20US%20and%20coalition%20forces%20against%20any%20threat%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20Gaza%20front%2C%20Israel%20continued%20attacking%20targets%20throughout%20Thursday.%20According%20to%20Israeli%20Army%20spokesperson%20Daniel%20Hagari%2C%20more%20than%205%2C000%20targets%20in%20G