mmed%20Deif%2C%26quot%3B%20in%20reference%20to%20the%20commander%20of%20Hamas's%20military%20wing%2C%20the%20Qassam%20Brigades.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20anger%20aimed%20at%20the%20Palestinian%20Authority%20is%20mainly%20due%20to%20the%20fact%20that%20it%20continues%20to%20cooperate%20with%20Israel%20on%20security-related%20issues.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20effort%20to%20prevent%20attacks%20from%20West%20Bank%20terror%20groups%2C%20Israeli%20security%20services%20have%20arrested%20an%20estimated%20850%20Palestinians%20since%20war%20broke%20out%20on%20October%207.%20According%20to%20the%20Israeli%20Army%20Spokesperson's%20office%2C%20the%20vast%20majority%20of%20those%20arrested%20have%20links%20to%20Hamas.%20But%20members%20of%20other%20Palestinian%20groups%20like%20The%20Lions%20Den%2C%20The%20Jenin%20Brigades%20and%20Islamic%20Jihad%20are%20also%20among%20the%20arrested.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20Israeli%20anti-terror%20raid%20on%20the%20Palestinian%20city%20of%20Tulkarem%2C%20at%20least%2013%20Palestinians%20were%20killed%20on%20Thursday.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Allan%20Sorensen%20is%20the%20Middle%20East%20correspondent%20for%20the%20Danish%20daily%20newspaper%20Kristeligt%20Dagblad.)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20the%20personal%20opinions%20of%20the%20author.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1697793240000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-10%2Fs5vhgii_daily-despatch_625x300_20_October_23.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fdaily-despatch-israel-and-hezbollah-move-closer-to-all-out-war-4499361%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20latest%20uptick%20in%20cross%20border%20attacks%20has%20ratcheted%20up%20tensions%20between%20Israel%20and%20Hezbollah.%20While%20each%20side%20still%20refrains%20from%20declaring%20a%20state%20of%20war%2C%20Israel%20has%20started%20evacuating%20some%2023.000%20citizens%20of%20Kiryat%20Shemona.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22