ere%20was%20the%20%3Cem%3Echai%20%3C%2Fem%3Ebusiness%20before%20I%20started%20the%20%3Cem%3Ekulhad%20%3C%2Fem%3Ebusiness.%20You%20never%20know%20what%20would%20hit%20the%20right%20nerve%20in%20the%20market%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESomething%20as%20simple%20as%20%3Cem%3Ekulhad%20%3C%2Fem%3Ehas%20helped%20Shobhit%20to%20earn%20crores%20while%20making%20a%20sustainable%20and%20eco-friendly%20product.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2Fkulhad-1-1697721886.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22With%20his%20kulhad%20business%2C%20Shobhit%20makes%20a%20whopping%20turnover%20of%20Rs%202.76%20crore%20per%20year%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2Fkulhad-1-1697721886.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2Fkulhad-1-1697721886-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2Fkulhad-1-1697721886-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2Fkulhad-1-1697721886-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2Fkulhad-1-1697721886-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-332626%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EWith%20his%20kulhad%20business%2C%20Shobhit%20makes%20a%20whopping%20turnover%20of%20Rs%202.76%20crore%20per%20year.%C2%A0Picture%20credit%3A%20Shobhit%20Soni%20%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CNo%20other%20cup%20%E2%80%94%20be%20it%20paper%20or%20glass%20%E2%80%94%20is%20as%20sustainable%20and%20eco-friendly%20as%20a%20clay%20cup.%20Even%20when%20we%20started%20our%20chai%20business%2C%20I%20was%20sure%20that%20I%20wanted%20to%2