20earned%20enough%20to%20pay%20their%20staff%20members%20their%20salary%2C%20which%20was%20one%20of%20the%20most%20rewarding%20moments%20in%20her%20life%2C%20says%20the%20businesswoman.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhen%20I%20was%20able%20to%20pay%20someone%20a%20salary%2C%20which%20was%20the%20same%20amount%20which%20I%20got%20in%20my%20first%20job%2C%20I%20felt%20so%20happy.%20What%20added%20to%20the%20happiness%20was%20the%20fact%20that%20it%20was%20from%20the%20profits%20and%20we%20didn%E2%80%99t%20have%20to%20take%20any%20loan%20or%20investment%20for%20the%20same%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBuoyed%20by%20the%20sales%2C%20they%20opened%20their%20second%20branch%20in%20Mumbai%20within%20six%20months.%20Today%2C%20they%20have%20eight%20branches%20across%20Mumbai%20and%20Hyderabad%2C%20with%20plans%20of%20opening%20three%20more%20in%20Hyderabad%20this%20month.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20COVID-19%20pandemic%20saw%20everyone%20moving%20to%20healthier%20consumption%20and%20one%20of%20the%20food%20items%20prescribed%20by%20doctors%20is%20always%20%3Cem%3Ekhichdi%3C%2Fem%3E%3B%20be%20it%20the%20dal%20khichdi%20in%20the%20north%20to%20your%20%3Cem%3Epongal%3C%2Fem%3E%20in%20the%20south.%20This%20saw%20a%20boom%20for%20businesses%20like%20Khichdi%20Express%2C%20as%20more%20people%20started%20ordering%20the%20dish.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20got%20a%20lot%20of%20orders%20from%20hospitals%2C%20isolation%20centres%20and%20people%20at%20home.%20We%20distributed%20free%20%3Cem%3Ekhichdi%3C%2Fem%3E%20to%20people%20on%20the%20streets%20of%20Mumbai.%20People%20would%20call%20us%20with%20instructions%20asking%20for%20less%20spices.%20They%20would%20call%20us%20after%20their%20family%20members%20recovered%20and%20thank%20us.%20It%20was%20a%20rewarding%20moment.%20We%20felt%20great%20as%20our%20food%20could%20heal%20people%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ELavanya%2C%20a%20%3Cem%3Ekhichdi%3C%2Fem%3E%20lover%20who%20stays%20in%20Banjara%20Hi